quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,104,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Imi vanhu! Kana musingagutsikane nechitendero changu (Islaam), nokudaro (zivai kuti) handifi ndakanamata izvo zvamunonamata kunze kwaAllah. Asi ndinonamata Allah vanoita kuti mufe, uye ndakakomekedzwa kuti ndive umwe wevatendi.”"
  10,105,"“Uye (zvadzikiswa kwandiri): ‘Tendeudza huso hwako (Muhammad (SAW)) kuchitendero cheHaneef (Islaam, kunamatwa kwaMwari mumwechete), uye zvirokwazvo usava umwe wemaMushrikoon (avo vanosanganisa Mwari nezvimwe zvinhu mukunamata).’"
  10,106,"‘Uye usava unodana chimwe chinhu kunze kwaAllah icho chisingakubatsiri kana kukukuvadza, asi kana ukadaro, zvirokwazvo uchava umwe wemaDhaalimoon (vanosanganisa Allah nezvimwe zvinhu mukunamata uye vatadzi).’”"
  10,107,"Uye kana Allah vakakubata nemarwadzo hakuna anokwanisa kuwabvisa kunze kwavo, uye kana vakakushuvira zvakanaka, hakuna anokwanisa kudzivirira chido chavo icho chavanenge vaita kuti chisvike kuna ani nani wevaranda vavo vavanenge vashuvira. Uye ndivo vane ruregerero rwose, nengoni dzose"
  10,108,"Iti: “Imi vanhu! Iyezvino chokwadi (Qur’aan namutumwa Muhammad (SAW)) chauya kwamuri kubva kuna Tenzi venyu. Nokudaro ani nani anogamuchira gwara, anodaro kuzvinatsurudza iye pachake; uye ani nani anorasika, anodaro mukurasikirwa kwake ega; uye handisi kwamuri muchengetedzi (anokumanikidzirai kutevera gwara).”"
  10,109,"Uye (iwe Muhammad (SAW)), tevedza zvaburutswa kwauri, uye iva nemoyo murefu kusvika Allah vapa mutongo. Uye ndivo vanogonesesa pavatongi (mutongi mukuru)"